Grid,is,a,scientific,instrument,for,the,study,of,large,scale,parallel,and,distributed,systems,The,suite,of,APIs,was,designed,to,ease,scripting,and,provide,better,access,to,the,grid,functionalities,A,description,of,the,APIs,follows,Metrology,API,Provides,the,key,metrics,of,the,Grid,nodes,memory,cpu,usage,bytes,in,bytes,out,Jobs,API,Allows,users,to,submit,jobs,on,a,Grid,site,Monitoring,API,Provides,the,status,of,the,Grid,nodes,Reference,API,Provides,the,reference,data,of,Grid,such,as,the,list,of,sites,clusters,nodes,environment,Deployments,API,Allows,users,to,deploy,a,specific,environment,on,Grid,nodes,Users,API,Offers,functionalities,to,manage,Grid,user,accounts,The,API,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML,JSON,PDF,and,HTML,Full,documentation,requires,registration